### Description

In the current implementation I cannot isolate the service or tokens for host directives

```ts
@Directive({
 // ...
 providers: [OptionsForOnlyMyDirective],
 hostDirectives: [
        {
            directive: MyDirective,
            inputs: ['options', 'open'],
            outputs: ['openChange'],
        },
    ],
})
```

### Proposed solution

```ts
@Directive({
 // ...
 hostDirectives: [
        {
            directive: MyDirective,
            inputs: ['options', 'open'],
            outputs: ['openChange'],
            providers: [OptionsForOnlyMyDirective]
        },
    ],
})
```

